<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Confirm Your Subscription - Build Fast with AI</title>
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/tailwindcss/2.2.19/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@500;600;700;800&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      background: #F9FAFB;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    
    h1, h2, h3 {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    }
    
    .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #059669, #d97706);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .bubble {
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #059669, #047857);
      padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      color: white;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: inline-block;
      transform: rotate(-2deg);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.2);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    
    .card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
    }
    
    .glow {
      position: absolute;
      width: 40%;
      height: 40%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.1) 0%, rgba(5, 150, 105, 0) 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    
    .step {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .step-number {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      width: 2rem;
      height: 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #059669, #047857);
      border-radius: 9999px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    
    .highlight-box {
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.1), rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.1));
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #059669;
    }
    
    .email-subject {
      background-color: rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.1);
      border-radius: 0.25rem;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
      font-family: monospace;
    }
    
    .email-screenshot {
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
      margin: 1.5rem auto;
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }
    
    .checklist-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: start;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .check-icon {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 1.5rem;
      height: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #059669, #047857);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-right: 1rem;
      margin-top: 0.125rem;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .support-text {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .support-email {
      color: #059669;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="relative min-h-screen">
    <!-- Background glows -->
    <div class="glow" style="top: -10%; right: -10%;"></div>
    <div class="glow" style="bottom: -10%; left: -10%;"></div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-4">
        <div class="bubble">
          Almost There!
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6">
          Check Your Email to <span class="gradient-text">Confirm Your Subscription</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">
          You're one step away from joining 1,000+ builders creating tools fast with AI.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-6">
            Here's what to do next:
          </h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">1</div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Check your inbox</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Look for an email with the subject: <span class="email-subject">
                  Confirm Now: Build Fast with AI Newsletter
                </span>
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">
                (If you don't see it, check your spam or promotions folder)
              </p>
              
              <div class="relative my-6">
                <img 
                  src="/images/newsletter-confirm.png" 
                  alt="Confirmation email example" 
                  class="email-screenshot"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">2</div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Open the email</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Find and click the "Confirm my subscription" button inside the email.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">3</div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">You're in!</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                You'll get immediate access to your AI building toolkit.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="highlight-box">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3">
              Here's what you'll get after confirming:
            </h3>
            <div class="checklist-item">
              <div class="check-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="font-medium">50+ ready-to-build prompts</span> to jumpstart your projects.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item">
              <div class="check-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="font-medium">My exact AI tool list</span> to build fast.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item">
              <div class="check-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="font-medium">Weekly build tutorials</span> to create games, SaaS products, landing pages, financial models, and more.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="support-text">
            Can't find the email? Contact <a href="mailto:support@backofnapkin.co" class="support-email">
              support@backofnapkin.co
            </a> and we'll help you out.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer class="py-8 text-center text-gray-500 text-sm">
      <p>Â© 2025 Build with AI. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>